caption.title: Seasonal pregnancy rate of A. agrarius and rainfall (mm).
caption.p: This data is from the Chencang district, adjacent to Hu County, and was collected between 1984–1987 [ 38]. The black line is the seasonal pregnancy rate of A. agrarius, and the blue line represents monthly rainfall (mm), 1984–1987. The pregnancy rate of A. agrarius was found to be correlated with rainfall (R = 0.60, P < 0.01).
